从2004年起，同性间的民事结合在巴西合法。2013年5月14日，巴西联邦法院裁定同性婚姻合法，该判决否定了联邦各州不认可同性婚姻的权利。2010年4月27日，[[巴西最高法院|巴西最高法院]]一致裁定，批准同性戀伴侶認養子女。2011年5月5日，巴西的最高法院以10比0的法官意見、一名法官缺席下裁定同性戀者之間的民事伴侶關係必須得到法律承認<ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2011/05/05/world/americas/AP-LT-Brazil-Civil-Unions.html?hp Brazil's Top Court Approves Civil Unions {{en icon}}]</ref>。巴西的羅馬天主教徒佔有相當大的人口比例。6月27日，巴西聖保羅州法官第一次裁定兩名男子的民事伴侶關係可轉為婚姻關係。2012年1月6日[[阿拉戈斯州|阿拉戈斯州]]法官判決以同性婚姻<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tjal.jus.br/corregedoria/provimentos/fdecf43ea5a3804e37b479be1b6a01e5.pdf|title=PROVIMENTO Nº 40, DE 06 DE DEZEMBRO DE 2011|last=JAMES|first=MAGALHÃES DE MEDEIROS|language=pt|accessdate=8 January 2012|archivedate=2012-01-08|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/64Y30IZ2Y?url=http://www.tjal.jus.br/corregedoria/provimentos/fdecf43ea5a3804e37b479be1b6a01e5.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="GU">{{cite web|url=http://acapa.virgula.uol.com.br/politica/alagoas-regulamenta-o-casamento-civil-entre-gays-em-todos-os-cartorios-do-estado/2/14/15493|title=Alagoas regulamenta o casamento civil entre gays em todos os cartórios do estado|last=Redação|first=Por|date=6 January 2012|publisher=guagh.com.br|language=pt|accessdate=7 January 2012|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/64XuyIuC5?url=http://acapa.virgula.uol.com.br/politica/alagoas-regulamenta-o-casamento-civil-entre-gays-em-todos-os-cartorios-do-estado/2/14/15493|archivedate=2012-01-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>代替民事結合<ref name="terra">{{cite web|url=http://noticias.terra.com.br/brasil/noticias/0,,OI5546036-EI306,00-Iniciativa+da+Justica+de+Alagoas+facilita+casamento+gay.html|title=Iniciativa da Justiça de Alagoas facilita casamento gay|date=6 January 2012|publisher=terra|language=pt|accessdate=7 January 2012|archivedate=2012-01-08|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/64XvARgOi?url=http://noticias.terra.com.br/brasil/noticias/0,,OI5546036-EI306,00-Iniciativa+da+Justica+de+Alagoas+facilita+casamento+gay.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，令該州成為巴西第一個承認同性婚姻的州份。<ref name="Correio">{{cite web|url=http://correiodobrasil.com.br/%C2%A0alagoas-facilita-casamento-de-homossexuais/352922/|title=Alagoas facilita casamento de homossexuais|last=Vermelho|first=Por|date=7 January 2012|publisher=Correio de Brasil|language=pt|accessdate=7 January 2012|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/64XvJrpCy?url=http://correiodobrasil.com.br/%C2%A0alagoas-facilita-casamento-de-homossexuais/352922/|archivedate=2012-01-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Jurídico">{{cite web|url=http://www.conjur.com.br/2012-jan-07/tjs-alagoas-espirito-santo-orientam-cartorios-registrar-uniao-gay|title=Justiça de AL e ES orientam cartórios sobre união gay|date=7 January 2012|publisher=Consultor Jurídico|language=pt|accessdate=7 January 2012|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/64XvNmBio?url=http://www.conjur.com.br/2012-jan-07/tjs-alagoas-espirito-santo-orientam-cartorios-registrar-uniao-gay|archivedate=2012-01-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年5月14日，巴西联邦司法委员会判决，负责核發结婚证书的政府单位无权拒绝同性伴侣登记结婚。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.estadao.com.br/noticias/cidades,cnj-obriga-cartorios-a-celebrar-casamento-entre-homossexuais,1031678,0.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-05-16 |archive-date=2014-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140121210215/http://www.estadao.com.br/noticias/cidades,cnj-obriga-cartorios-a-celebrar-casamento-entre-homossexuais,1031678,0.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.france24.com/en/20130514-brazil-judicial-panel-clears-way-gay-marriage |title=Brazil judicial panel clears way for gay marriage |access-date=2013-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130609172419/http://www.france24.com/en/20130514-brazil-judicial-panel-clears-way-gay-marriage |archive-date=2013-06-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2013/05/15/world/americas/brazil-same-sex-marriage/index.html?eref=edition |title=Brazilian judicial council orders notaries to recognize same-sex marriage |accessdate=2013-05-16 |archive-date=2017-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171225034902/http://edition.cnn.com/2013/05/15/world/americas/brazil-same-sex-marriage/index.html?eref=edition |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.enca.com/world/brazil-clears-way-gay-marriage |title=Brazil clears way for gay marriage |accessdate=2013-05-16 |archive-date=2018-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180707120758/http://www.enca.com/world/brazil-clears-way-gay-marriage |dead-url=no }}</ref>这项裁定是5月15日发布，并于2013年5月16日生效。<ref>{{pt}} [http://www.cnj.jus.br/dje/jsp/dje/DownloadDeDiario.jsp?dj=DJ89_2013-ASSINADO.PDF&statusDoDiario=ASSINADO DIÁRIO DA JUSTIÇA CONSELHO NACIONAL DE JUSTIÇA Edição nº 89/2013] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnj.jus.br/dje/jsp/dje/DownloadDeDiario.jsp?dj=DJ89_2013-ASSINADO.PDF&statusDoDiario=ASSINADO |date=20130927065724 }}</ref><ref>{{pt}} [http://g1.globo.com/politica/noticia/2013/05/regra-que-obriga-cartorios-fazer-casamento-gay-vale-partir-do-dia-16.html Regra que obriga cartórios a fazer casamento gay vale a partir do dia 16] {{Wayback|url=http://g1.globo.com/politica/noticia/2013/05/regra-que-obriga-cartorios-fazer-casamento-gay-vale-partir-do-dia-16.html |date=20190419152629 }}</ref>巴西因而成为全世界第15个保障同性婚姻的国家，并且是拉美地区第三个也是最大的一个保障婚姻平等权利的国家。

